# =============================================================================
# ClawBench Agent Configuration Example — DeepSeek Backend
# ClawBench 智能体配置示例 — DeepSeek 后端
# =============================================================================
#
# DeepSeek TUI — supports extended thinking and multi-turn conversation.
# DeepSeek TUI — 支持深度思考和多轮对话。
#
# Model discovery: DeepSeek models are auto-discovered via `deepseek models`
# command at runtime. No need to manually list models.
# 模型发现：DeepSeek 模型通过 `deepseek models` 命令在运行时自动发现，无需手动列出。
#
# This file is NOT loaded (the .yaml.example extension is ignored by LoadAgents).
# 本文件不会被加载（.yaml.example 后缀会被 LoadAgents 忽略）。
# To use, copy as e.g. my-deepseek-agent.yaml and modify the config.
# 实际使用时请复制为如 my-deepseek-agent.yaml 并修改配置。
# =============================================================================

id: deepseek
name: DeepSeek TUI
icon: 🔍
specialty: DeepSeek 推理与编码 — 支持深度思考和多轮对话
backend: deepseek

# Models are auto-discovered via `deepseek models`. To override, uncomment:
# models:
#   - id: deepseek-v4-flash
#     name: DeepSeek V4 Flash
#     default: true
#   - id: deepseek-v4-pro
#     name: DeepSeek V4 Pro

system_prompt: |
  You are a versatile assistant powered by DeepSeek, capable of handling code, documentation, operations, research, and various tasks.
